{"eval_id": "financebench_id_00995", "question": "What are the major products and services that AMD sells as of FY22?", "pred_answer": "AMD作为 of FY22 的主要产品和 services 包括：\n1. **x86 微处理器（CPU）** 和 **图形处理单元（GPU）**，作为独立设备或集成到加速处理单元（APU）中。\n2. **芯片组**、**数据中心及专业 GPU**、**嵌入式处理器**、**半定制 System-on-Chip（SoC）产品**。\n3. **数据处理单元（DPU）**、**现场可编程门阵列（FPGA）**、**自适应 SoC 产品**。\n4. **微处理器及 SoC 开发服务与技术**。\n5. **知识产权（IP）授权**（部分技术或专利）。\n\n此外，AMD 通过直接销售、分销商、OEM 合作伙伴及增值经销商（VARs/ISVs）等渠道推广上述产品。", "pred_doc_names": ["AMD_2022_10K"], "pred_chunks": [{"chunk_id": 115, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 11, "page_end": 11, "score": 0.485}, {"chunk_id": 141, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 14, "page_end": 14, "score": 0.478291}, {"chunk_id": 736, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 60, "page_end": 60, "score": 0.457822}, {"chunk_id": 114, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 11, "page_end": 11, "score": 0.4268}, {"chunk_id": 116, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 11, "page_end": 11, "score": 0.4268}], "error": "", "doc_hit_at_1": 1, "doc_hit_at_5": 1, "doc_mrr": 1.0, "chunk_hit_at_1": null, "chunk_hit_at_5": null, "chunk_mrr": null, "page_hit_at_5": 0, "numeric_match": 0, "normalized_exact_match": 0, "answer_label": "partial", "must_include_hit_ratio": 1.0, "answer_correctness": null, "answer_groundedness": null, "answer_completeness": null, "gold_doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "gold_pages": [3], "gold_chunk_ids": [], "gold_chunk_status": "unresolved", "gold_chunk_match_method": ""}
{"eval_id": "financebench_id_01198", "question": "What drove revenue change as of the FY22 for AMD?", "pred_answer": "AMD 2022财年收入增长主要由以下因素驱动：\n1. **数据中心业务增长64%**，因EPYC™服务器处理器销量增加；\n2. **游戏业务增长21%**，因半定制产品销售提升；\n3. **嵌入式业务显著增长**，受益于Xilinx嵌入式产品收入的并表（收购Xilinx于2022年2月）。\n同时，**客户端业务下降10%**（受PC市场需求疲软及库存调整影响）部分抵消了增长。", "pred_doc_names": ["AMD_2022_10K"], "pred_chunks": [{"chunk_id": 545, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 43, "page_end": 43, "score": 0.515406}, {"chunk_id": 748, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 61, "page_end": 61, "score": 0.493546}, {"chunk_id": 646, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 49, "page_end": 49, "score": 0.482009}, {"chunk_id": 544, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 43, "page_end": 43, "score": 0.453557}, {"chunk_id": 546, "doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "page_start": 43, "page_end": 43, "score": 0.453557}], "error": "", "doc_hit_at_1": 1, "doc_hit_at_5": 1, "doc_mrr": 1.0, "chunk_hit_at_1": null, "chunk_hit_at_5": null, "chunk_mrr": null, "page_hit_at_5": 0, "numeric_match": 0, "normalized_exact_match": 0, "answer_label": "partial", "must_include_hit_ratio": 1.0, "answer_correctness": null, "answer_groundedness": null, "answer_completeness": null, "gold_doc_name": "AMD_2022_10K", "gold_pages": [42], "gold_chunk_ids": [], "gold_chunk_status": "unresolved", "gold_chunk_match_method": ""}
